legend: |md
  **Legend**
  - **Blue**: internal feature → shared dependency
  - **Green**: leaf-layer (utils, internal/svg)
  - **Dashed pink**: external dependency (templ used by all; tailwind-merge-go by utils; go-error-family by errorpage)
  - **utils**: 0 fan-out (true leaf), 204 in-edges (hub)
  - **No cycles. Max fan-out: 5 (display).**
